{"id":199926,"date":[{"year":1950,"month":10,"day":15}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"368","ytitle":"","mtitle":"一个鸡蛋","ftitle":"——爱民小故事","authors":["亚平"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>沙漠</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>亚平　词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙漠　图</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\10\\50af051101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(一)一九六团马子新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因有工作出外行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没把房门关得紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两双鸡子钻进门。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\10\\50af051102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(二)鸡子马上跳上坑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东抓西抓抓的忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓乱稻草散满地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还撒鸡屎在大坑上。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\10\\50af051103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(三)马子新　爱整洁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回家一看动了气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握紧拳头要出房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想一拳揍死那两只鸡。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\10\\50af051104.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(四)同志们忙劝马子新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“上级动员爱人民”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马子新自己也想了想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“群众纪律顶要紧”。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\10\\50af051105.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(五)马子新怒气散，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫地整坑不怕烦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫清鸡屎理好草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱草下发现个大鸡蛋</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\10\\50af051106.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(六)马子新如果凭着火气干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早就丢掉这大鸡蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想着了，群众纪律要做好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是把鸡蛋送还老太太，</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\10\\50af051107.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(七)马子新，把蛋快快去送到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老太太，心里欢喜脸带笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两只手，接了鸡蛋点点头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连声说，解放军同志真正好。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1950\\10\\50af051108.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>(八)全班同志知道了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说这事做得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响了号召守纪律，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老马真是个模范太好佬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(注:时间发生在舟山解放前，因此，解放军仍穿旧制服)</FONT>"}]}